snippet.title: Hollow Knight - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/367520/
Pre-order on Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/hollow-knight
Site: http://www.hollowknight.com
Wishlist on GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/hollow_knight

On February 24th descend into a world of Insects and Heroes in Hollow Knight for PC & Mac!

Get the Soundtrack at:
https://christopherlarkin.bandcamp.com/album/hollow-knight-original-soundtrack
